{"tid":1021929,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[衝燈之嘛，都未撞]荃灣綫新信號系統測試出現列車「越燈」　港鐵：不罕見","createTime":"2019-02-14T14:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T01:19:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b496170c4f218b0e0abac9eaa0117a8e97887ec9","tid":1021929,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442890-20190214.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442890-20190214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDl9PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=0914aea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442890-20190214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de253e8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442890-20190214.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵證實，荃灣綫新信號系統測試期間，一度出現列車「越燈」情況，但港鐵強調，新信號系統採用安全防護保障設計，測試時亦正常運作，事件沒有構成任何安全影響。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，港鐵荃灣綫本月10日凌晨，一列裝有新信號系統的列車駛離月台後，未有自動停於指定信號燈的前方，車長要緊急剎車。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵表示，新信號系統測試期間，「越燈」情況偶有發生並不罕見，同時亦是測試目的，因爲可以收集數據分析，為信號系統的穩定性作更精準的安排。 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"87e835d50b67a3102f11f3a2ec06f5862a0e5059","tid":1021929,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"鋼根扭唔入都冇問題啦 區區越燈點會有嘢"},{"pid":"39c207944d3f5a1b78aa55ce0f8f69ce921d4589","tid":1021929,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"又黎你話OK就OK"},{"pid":"148fcfb3b44453f7cd1ec7d8be4c6ac5c4da3643","tid":1021929,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:19:29.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，新信號系統測試期間，「越燈」情況偶有發生並不罕見，同時亦是測試目的，因爲可以收集數據分析，為信號系統的穩定性作更精準的安排。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face